<br>
Guildies will get free combines.  The guildies who I like and treat me with respect, I do combines in a timely fashion and also will supply ingredients they always seem to forget.  Guildies who bother me all the time and ask what the recipe is for every single little thing in the world will get a &quot;goto EQTraders and supply me with every single ingredient.&quot;<br>
<br>
Respect goes a long way.  I've done many free combines for strangers who are nice about it and say &quot;please&quot; and &quot;thank you&quot; and use complete sentences with correct grammar.  If people offer, I'll usually take it.<br>
<br>
But it all depends on my mood.  But in general if it is an item that I know for sure a person will use, I will be nice.<br>
<br>
Shjinn<br>
